    "en": {
      "title": "Jaffa who tried to smuggle ice drugs. Arrested in the city",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "A person was arrested by the Urgavarurai police for possessing the drug ice in Jaffna city.",
        "The suspect was arrested this evening near Manippai Road Chatrachandi, Jaffna.",
        "A 46-year-old man from the five-storey area of \u200b\u200bGurunagar, Jaffna was arrested in this way.",
        "The police said that the arrest was made with the help of the Military Intelligence Unit based on the information received by the Urgawariura police."
      ],
